<svg viewBox="0 0 700 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Seçim Körlüğü Dört Adımda Nasıl İşler</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Üç deney, üç alan — aynı örüntü</text>
  <rect x="30" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="105" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">①</text>
  <text x="105" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Gerçek seçim</text>
  <text x="105" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">enflasyon koruması olarak</text>
  <line x1="180" y1="130" x2="194" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="194,125 200,130 194,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="200" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="275" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">②</text>
  <text x="275" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Sessiz değişim</text>
  <text x="275" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">tez sessizce değişir</text>
  <line x1="350" y1="130" x2="364" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="364,125 370,130 364,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="370" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="445" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">③</text>
  <text x="445" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Değişmiş sonuç verilir</text>
  <text x="445" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">hâlâ tutuyor, farklı gerekçe</text>
  <line x1="520" y1="130" x2="534" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="534,125 540,130 534,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="540" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="615" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">④</text>
  <text x="615" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Kendinden emin gerekçe</text>
  <text x="615" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">hep böyle olduğuna inanır</text>
  <text x="350" y="225" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Fark edilmeme — yüzlerde %87'ye kadar · reçelde %67+ · ahlaki inançlarda %69</text>
  <text x="350" y="250" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Johansson et al. 2005 · Hall et al. 2010 · Hall, Johansson &amp; Strandberg 2012</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="vi">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Mù Lựa Chọn Vận Hành Qua Bốn Bước</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Ba thí nghiệm, ba lĩnh vực — cùng một mô hình</text>
  <rect x="30" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="105" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">①</text>
  <text x="105" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Lựa chọn thực tế</text>
  <text x="105" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">mua để chống lạm phát</text>
  <line x1="180" y1="130" x2="194" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="194,125 200,130 194,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="200" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="275" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">②</text>
  <text x="275" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Tráo đổi âm thầm</text>
  <text x="275" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">luận điểm âm thầm thay đổi</text>
  <line x1="350" y1="130" x2="364" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="364,125 370,130 364,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="370" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="445" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">③</text>
  <text x="445" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Nhận kết quả bị tráo</text>
  <text x="445" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">vẫn giữ, lý do khác</text>
  <line x1="520" y1="130" x2="534" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="534,125 540,130 534,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="540" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="615" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">④</text>
  <text x="615" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Biện minh đầy tự tin</text>
  <text x="615" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">tin rằng vẫn luôn như vậy</text>
  <text x="350" y="225" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Không phát hiện — khuôn mặt đến 87% · mứt hơn 67% · niềm tin đạo đức 69%</text>
  <text x="350" y="250" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Johansson et al. 2005 · Hall et al. 2010 · Hall, Johansson &amp; Strandberg 2012</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="id">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Bagaimana Kebutaan Pilihan Bekerja dalam Empat Langkah</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Tiga eksperimen, tiga bidang — pola yang sama</text>
  <rect x="30" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="105" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">①</text>
  <text x="105" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Pilihan sebenarnya</text>
  <text x="105" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">dibeli sebagai lindung nilai inflasi</text>
  <line x1="180" y1="130" x2="194" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="194,125 200,130 194,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="200" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="275" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">②</text>
  <text x="275" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Pertukaran diam-diam</text>
  <text x="275" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">tesis berubah diam-diam</text>
  <line x1="350" y1="130" x2="364" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="364,125 370,130 364,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="370" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="445" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">③</text>
  <text x="445" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Diberi hasil yang ditukar</text>
  <text x="445" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">tetap memegang, alasan berbeda</text>
  <line x1="520" y1="130" x2="534" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="534,125 540,130 534,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="540" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="615" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">④</text>
  <text x="615" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Justifikasi penuh keyakinan</text>
  <text x="615" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">percaya selalu begitu sejak awal</text>
  <text x="350" y="225" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Tidak terdeteksi — wajah hingga 87% · selai hingga 67%+ · keyakinan moral 69%</text>
  <text x="350" y="250" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Johansson et al. 2005 · Hall et al. 2010 · Hall, Johansson &amp; Strandberg 2012</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="pl">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Jak Ślepota Wyboru Działa w Czterech Krokach</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Trzy eksperymenty, trzy dziedziny — ten sam wzorzec</text>
  <rect x="30" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="105" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">①</text>
  <text x="105" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Rzeczywisty wybór</text>
  <text x="105" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">kupione jako zabezpieczenie przed inflacją</text>
  <line x1="180" y1="130" x2="194" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="194,125 200,130 194,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="200" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="275" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">②</text>
  <text x="275" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Cicha podmiana</text>
  <text x="275" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">teza cicho się zmienia</text>
  <line x1="350" y1="130" x2="364" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="364,125 370,130 364,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="370" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="445" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">③</text>
  <text x="445" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Otrzymany zamieniony wynik</text>
  <text x="445" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">wciąż trzyma, inny powód</text>
  <line x1="520" y1="130" x2="534" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="534,125 540,130 534,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="540" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="615" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">④</text>
  <text x="615" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Pewne siebie uzasadnienie</text>
  <text x="615" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">wierzy, że zawsze tak było</text>
  <text x="350" y="225" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Brak wykrycia — twarze do 87% · dżem do 67%+ · przekonania moralne 69%</text>
  <text x="350" y="250" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Johansson et al. 2005 · Hall et al. 2010 · Hall, Johansson &amp; Strandberg 2012</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="it">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Come la Cecità della Scelta Si Svolge in Quattro Fasi</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Tre esperimenti, tre ambiti — lo stesso schema</text>
  <rect x="30" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="105" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">①</text>
  <text x="105" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Scelta reale</text>
  <text x="105" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">acquistato come copertura anti-inflazione</text>
  <line x1="180" y1="130" x2="194" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="194,125 200,130 194,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="200" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="275" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">②</text>
  <text x="275" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Scambio silenzioso</text>
  <text x="275" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">la tesi cambia silenziosamente</text>
  <line x1="350" y1="130" x2="364" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="364,125 370,130 364,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="370" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="445" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">③</text>
  <text x="445" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Riceve il risultato scambiato</text>
  <text x="445" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">continua a detenere, motivo diverso</text>
  <line x1="520" y1="130" x2="534" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="534,125 540,130 534,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="540" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="615" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">④</text>
  <text x="615" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Giustificazione sicura</text>
  <text x="615" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">crede che sia sempre stato così</text>
  <text x="350" y="225" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Mancato rilevamento — volti fino all'87% · marmellata fino al 67%+ · convinzioni morali 69%</text>
  <text x="350" y="250" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Johansson et al. 2005 · Hall et al. 2010 · Hall, Johansson &amp; Strandberg 2012</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="ru">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Как Слепота Выбора Работает в Четыре Шага</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Три эксперимента, три области — одна и та же закономерность</text>
  <rect x="30" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="105" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">①</text>
  <text x="105" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Реальный выбор</text>
  <text x="105" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">куплено как хедж от инфляции</text>
  <line x1="180" y1="130" x2="194" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="194,125 200,130 194,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="200" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="275" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">②</text>
  <text x="275" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Тихая подмена</text>
  <text x="275" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">тезис тихо меняется</text>
  <line x1="350" y1="130" x2="364" y2="130" stroke="#52525b" stroke-width="2"/>
  <polygon points="364,125 370,130 364,135" fill="#52525b"/>
  <rect x="370" y="70" width="150" height="120" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,.12)" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="445" y="95" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="20" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">③</text>
  <text x="445" y="125" fill="#f4f4f5" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Получен подменённый результат</text>
  <text x="445" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">всё ещё держит, другая причина</text>
